Package: bfrms
Title: Bayes Factors for Bayesian Regression Models using 'Stan'
Version: 0.1-0
Authors@R: c(person(given="Henrik", family="Singmann", role=c("aut", "cre"),
             email="singmann@gmail.com",
             comment=c(ORCID="0000-0002-4842-3657")),
             person(given="Quentin F.", family="Gronau", role="aut",
             comment=c(ORCID="0000-0001-5510-6943")),
             person(given="Eric-Jan", family="Wagenmakers", role="ctb"))
Description: Allows estimation of (Gaussian) brms 
    <https://cran.r-project.org/package=brms> models using the JZS 
    (Jeffreys-Zellner-Siow) prior following Rouder, Morey, Speckman, and 
    Province (2012, <doi:10.1016/j.jmp.2012.08.001>). With these models it is 
    easy to obtain Bayes factors using the bridgesampling 
    <https://cran.r-project.org/package=bridgesampling> package. 
